refentry.refsect1:
Description
voidvar_dump mixedexpression mixedexpression ...
This function displays structured information about one or more expressions that includes its type and value. Arrays and objects are explored recursively with values indented to show structure.
In PHP 5 only public, private and protected properties of objects will be returned in the output.
&tip.ob-capture;
var_dump example
<?php $a = array (1, 2, array ("a", "b", "c")); var_dump($a); ?>
&example.outputs;
array(3) { [0]=> int(1) [1]=> int(2) [2]=> array(3) { [0]=> string(1) "a" [1]=> string(1) "b" [2]=> string(1) "c" } }
<?php
$b = 3.1; $c = true; var_dump($b, $c);
?>
&example.outputs;
float(3.1) bool(true)
See also var_export and print_r.
